.php?ID=28138|archive-date= 2012-10-06|df= }}</ref>\n\n==Awards==\n*1993 AVN Award \u2013 Best Packaging (Film) \u2013 ''Sin City - The Movie''<ref name=AVN9394>{{cite web|url=http://www.avnawards.com/pastwinners.shtml |title=Past Winners |access-date=2014-10-22 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050305121854/http://www.avnawards.com/pastwinners.shtml |archive-date=March 5, 2005 }}</ref>\n*1994 AVN Award \u2013 Best Packaging (Video) \u2013 ''Hungry''<ref name=AVN9394/>\n*1996 AVN Award \u2013 Best Gang Bang Tape \u2013 ''30 Men For Sandy''<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.rame.net/faq/avn/1995.html|title= Adult Video News Award Winners - 1995|accessdate= 2014-10-22|date= 1996-01-08|publisher= RAME}}</ref>\n*1999 AVN Award \u2013 Best Actor (Film) \u2013 ''Models'' (James Bonn)<ref name=AVN99>{{cite magazine|url=http://avn.com/awards/winners.html |title=Last Year's Winner's |access-date=2014-10-22 |magazine=[[AVN (magazine)|AVN]] |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19991013062528/http://avn.com/awards/winners.html |archive-date=October 13, 1999 }}</ref>\n*1999 AVN Award \u2013 Best Supporting Actor (Film) \u2013 ''Models'' ([[Michael J. Cox]])<ref name=AVN99/>\n*2000 AVN Award \u2013 Best Actor (Film) \u2013 ''Chloe'' (James Bonn)<ref name=AVN00>{{cite magazine|url= http://business.avn.com/articles/video/2000-AVN-Award-Winners-Announced-34398.html|title= 2000 AVN Award Winners Announced|accessdate= 2014-10-22|date= 2000-01-17|magazine= [[AVN (magazine)|AVN]]}}</ref>\n*2000 AVN Award \u2013 Best Actress (Film) \u2013 ''Chloe'' (Chloe)<ref name=AVN00/>\n*2001 AVN Award \u2013 Best Editing (Film) \u2013 ''Watchers'' ([[Michael Raven]] & Sammy Slater)<ref name=AVN01>{{cite web|url= http://www.ainews.com/Archives/Story1402.phtml|title= The AVN Awards Show a Night to Remember|accessdate= 2014-10-22|author= Steve Nelson|date= 2001-01-09|publisher= Adult Industry News}}</ref>\n*2001 AVN Award \u2013 Best Screenplay (Film) \u2013 